  "text": "Pain intensity and pain disability were assessed with two subscales of the BPI, [CITATION_1] the pain intensity subscale (four items), and limitations because of pain (seven items). [CITATION_2] The BPI has an 11-point Likert scale (range 0-10). Reliability of both subscales is satisfactory (pain intensity, Cronbach's α: 0.85; disability, Cronbach's α: 0.88).",
